    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093990/extras/d7de6ed692c530da11b882a19120476b.webp?t=1771404944\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093990/extras/d7de6ed692c530da11b882a19120476b.poster.avif?t=1771404944\" class=\"bb_img\" width=610 height=200 /></picture></span>《烈焰岛》是一款快节奏多人竞技游戏，最多四名玩家将操纵特性各异的火焰，在瞬息万变的动态地图上展开霸权争夺！胜利条件？收集地图上随机刷新的虚幻火焰——<i><strong>灵焰</strong></i>，来统治全岛！抢先点燃地块建立控制权——若未能在限定回合内完成，地块控制权或将易主。当资源逐渐枯竭、策略激烈碰撞，唯有最狡黠的火焰能够存续！<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093990/extras/de8caf3cdd35f174adb6a499f171306c.avif?t=1771404944\" width=610 height=475 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093990/extras/3895f9b734c2497e9bd6fb82fb5c341e.avif?t=1771404944\" width=608 height=80 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093990/extras/374b4855ad7a3a6093aa02d68e2e0a9d.poster.avif?t=1771404944\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093990/extras/374b4855ad7a3a6093aa02d68e2e0a9d.webm?t=1771404944\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>单人磨炼技艺，或参与最多四人在线混战！围堵对手、抢占最多领地、收集灵焰，直至最强火焰加冕！凭借快节奏玩法与动态策略，《烈焰岛》堪称热衷算计与背刺好友的玩家必玩之作。是联合压制领先者？直取灵焰？还是趁友军分心时，突袭封锁其火焰阵地？全由你决定！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093990/extras/62243fc265b0855f8a28bb2d32880b27.avif?t=1771404944\" width=608 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093990/extras/839ee5062f12fc30933f18b252f4ef9a.poster.avif?t=1771404944\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093990/extras/839ee5062f12fc30933f18b252f4ef9a.webm?t=1771404944\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >点燃地块需消耗<i><strong>火花</strong></i>，纵火狂的必备资源！毕竟，没有火花，何谈纵火？成功点燃的地块每回合会为你稳定产出火花。如果说火花是火焰的燃料，那么<i><strong>灰烬</strong></i>便是野心的资本！火焰终将熄灭，但灰烬可为你所用！使用灰烬可发动毁灭性技能、获取强力升级，甚至在对手松懈时实施破坏！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093990/extras/6671d8623d455e23792bc1fbf9629de7.avif?t=1771404944\" width=608 height=90 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093990/extras/5954fea8073a81775536a6a0e0523b08.poster.avif?t=1771404944\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093990/extras/5954fea8073a81775536a6a0e0523b08.webm?t=1771404944\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >时刻谨记岛屿地形的诡谲多变——其危险程度不亚于你的对手！引燃爆炸性<i><strong>煤矿层</strong></i>、激活可喷发烈焰的<i><strong>火山</strong></i>，甚至消耗灰烬熔穿<i><strong>雪原</strong>、<strong>沙地</strong></i>，与<i><strong>山岳</strong></i>！随着可占领地块逐渐减少，及时调整战略、善用环境要素才是制胜关键！ <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093990/extras/c4c8feefad251b160e648524b16283c1.avif?t=1771404944\" width=608 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以下功能正在紧锣密鼓开发中，也将成为《烈焰岛》正式版的亮点玩法！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><i><strong>灵焰系统</strong></i></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如前文所述，灵焰是胜利的关键，夺取它们需要迅捷反应与精准操作。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093990/extras/e249dd5a75c263451c3aa6e489fa5845.poster.avif?t=1771404944\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093990/extras/e249dd5a75c263451c3aa6e489fa5845.webm?t=1771404944\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><i><strong>职业与卡牌</strong></i></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >六种 RPG 风格职业即将登场，每个职业都有独有技能与颠覆战局的强化选项，等待玩家精通！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><i><strong>职业：</strong></i></u></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><i><strong>风暴术士</strong></i></u>——暴雨专精</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不仅能在雨中屹立，还能如鱼得水！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >能随意召唤暴风雨</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><i><strong>灵焰猎手</strong></i></u>——灵焰专精</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >摒弃华而不实的手段，专注灵焰收集之道</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >能以适当代价直接获取灵焰……</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><i><strong>陷阱大师</strong></i></u>——陷阱专精</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >基础陷阱人人会用，但此职业将陷阱玩法推向极致！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用源源不断的强力陷阱，让对手寸步难行！</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><i><strong>无拘旅者</strong></i></u>——移动专精</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><i><strong>无拘旅者</strong></i></u>——移动专精</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可投掷火焰跨越敌方防线，并具备被动火焰蔓延能力！</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可投掷火焰跨越敌方防线，并具备被动火焰蔓延能力！</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >何须亲自点火？夺取敌焰化为己用！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >能将敌方火焰据为己有！</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><i><strong>地形支配者</strong></i></u>——环境专精</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在沙地、岩层、雪原等艰难地形中游刃有余！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在沙地、岩层、雪原等艰难地形中游刃有余！</p></li></ul></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><i><strong>卡牌：</strong></i></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家可在回合间从三张<i><strong>卡牌</strong></i>中选择一张，打造瞬息万变的强力组合！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多数<i><strong>卡牌</strong></i>提供可叠加的基础增益；而<i><strong>金色卡牌</strong></i>虽极为稀有，却能带来与职业特性相辅相成的突破性强化！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093990/extras/7e4a56ac1c4e76c9b710e74bd09a7078.poster.avif?t=1771404944\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093990/extras/7e4a56ac1c4e76c9b710e74bd09a7078.webm?t=1771404944\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><i><strong>道具箱</strong></i></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>道具箱</strong></i>可能在回合间随机出现，带来意想不到的强力效果：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>火花解放</strong></i>——暂时移除火花上限，释放你的全部潜能！</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>凛冬寒锋</strong></i>——大幅提高对手点燃地块所需的火花消耗，阻滞他们的进展！</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>火焰伞盖</strong></i>——抵御雨水的侵袭，保护你的火焰！</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>首席灭火官</strong></i>——削弱领先玩家的火花获取，效果可叠加！</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>灰烬堆</strong></i>——火焰燃尽时，灰烬获取量翻倍。灵活使用，助你奠定胜局！</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>陷阱女王</strong></i>——放置陷阱的灰烬成本减半，让你尽情布置致命陷阱！</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>瓶中闪电</strong></i>——重置闪电冷却时间，让你的火焰在岛上重燃！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
